  </p>
  <p style="margin-top:28px;color:#5A5C63">Need legal help now? Call <a href="tel:+923363120798" style="color:#8A3A4A;font-weight:700">0336 3120798</a> or message us on <a href="https://wa.me/923363120798" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#1FA855;font-weight:700">WhatsApp</a>.</p>
</main>
<Footer />
